Laugh Riot with Kevin Hart

Type: Stand-up Comedy Show

Date and Time: November 30, 2025, 7:00 PM

Location: Dolby Theatre, Los Angeles

Details:
Kevin Hart brings his unique brand of humor to Los Angeles for one night only. Covering hilarious anecdotes from his personal life and sharp observations about current events, this show is guaranteed to leave you in stitches. Suitable for ages 18+.

Highlights: Live stand-up comedy, interactive audience engagement, exclusive meet-and-greet tickets.
